Class EntityTrackerHook

  • public class EntityTrackerHook
extends com.bergerkiller.mountiplex.reflection.ClassHook<EntityTrackerHook>
    This hook is used to spawn entities without creating an entity tracker entry. It is only temporarily hooked for the duration of a single Entity spawn.
